1
00:01:31,275 --> 00:01:36,102
<i>[Flourished Peony]</i>

2
00:01:36,102 --> 00:01:39,387
<i>[Episode 1]</i>

3
00:01:44,576 --> 00:01:47,282
<i>[Luoyang]</i>

4
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,560
The son of the Liu family is getting married.

5
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,919
What a grand spectacle!

6
00:02:29,919 --> 00:02:32,360
What kind of family background
does this bride have?

7
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,120
I've heard she's a merchant's daughter.

8
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,560
No one knows how she managed
to get connected to the Liu family.

9
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,120
The bride has arrived.

10
00:03:42,304 --> 00:03:43,392
<i>[Winter Donkey-hide Gelatin]</i>

11
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,479
Six boxes of jewelry and trinkets.

12
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:06,280
Three boxes of precious medicinal herbs.

13
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:11,479
Five boxes of brocades. Gold and jade…

14
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:13,240
How can your family be like this?

15
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,560
The bride is still here.

16
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:15,599
This is outrageous.

17
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,496
Yulu.

18
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,399
A maid.

19
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,576
My lady.

20
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,744
Be careful.

21
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,879
Why don't I hear any guests moving?

22
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,680
There's not a single guest in the house.

23
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:52,279
All the Liu family members are gathered
around our dowry, busy with their abacuses.

24
00:04:53,279 --> 00:04:55,000
The groom isn't coming
on horseback to welcome the bride.

25
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,680
It's already against the etiquettes.

26
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,160
Now they're not even setting up the banquet.

27
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,600
They even made us enter
through the back courtyard.

28
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,879
You can't treat the bride with such neglect.

29
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,639
Your mother is bedridden.

30
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:10,879
Your father is busy taking care of her.

31
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:13,639
We know that you are a filial child.

32
00:05:13,639 --> 00:05:15,279
You're certainly worried and anxious.

33
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:17,160
You wouldn't be in the mood
to deal with guests.

34
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,000
That's why there isn't a grand celebration.

35
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,480
I don't care about these empty formalities.

36
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:26,519
Everything is up to your decision.

37
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:30,800
My lord, we're ready.

38
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:36,839
Now is the auspicious time.

39
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:38,920
Please ask the groom to go to the main hall.

40
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,992
Yes.

41
00:05:57,639 --> 00:05:59,519
Dusk.

42
00:06:08,759 --> 00:06:10,639
Dusk.

43
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:19,680
Getting drunk like this
on the day of your wedding.

44
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:21,199
How reckless!

45
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:22,319
Hurry over and pay your respects.

46
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,199
It's you who are happy,

47
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,199
not me.

48
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:28,279
Liu Zishu!

49
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,839
My lord,

50
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:31,439
don't get angry.

51
00:06:31,439 --> 00:06:33,439
Zishu has always been courteous
and well-mannered.

52
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,959
Today he is being forced into marriage.

53
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,439
It's normal for him to be a bit temperamental.

54
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,439
Qiushi,

55
00:06:38,439 --> 00:06:39,879
quickly help the groom over here.

56
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,632
Mr. Zishu.

57
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:48,759
Mr. Zishu.

58
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,480
- Kneel down.
- Kneel down.

59
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:56,519
Bow before the mirror.

60
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:07,319
Husband and wife unite,
forever blessed and prosperous.

61
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:36,160
Hasn't the groom arrived yet?

62
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,120
Not even a shadow in sight.

63
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,639
You are clearly the principal wife.

64
00:07:41,639 --> 00:07:43,439
Yet you cannot enter his main chamber.

65
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:45,600
You're merely arranged to stay
in this secluded courtyard.

66
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:48,480
Isn't it just disdain for our merchant origins?

67
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,120
Your family runs
over a dozen herbal medicine shops.

68
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,120
Since childhood, you have been

69
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,399
surrounded by piles of gold and jade.

70
00:07:54,399 --> 00:07:55,879
Never have you suffered such grievances.

71
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,839
It's almost midnight,
I'll go look for Mr. Zishu.

72
00:08:02,079 --> 00:08:03,399
Mr. Zishu.

73
00:08:03,399 --> 00:08:04,920
I tell you, He Weifang,

74
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:06,680
if it weren't for my father

75
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,759
relying on this dowry

76
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:09,360
to alleviate the urgent need,

77
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,360
you would have no chance

78
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,839
to attach yourself to our Liu family.

79
00:08:11,839 --> 00:08:13,360
- Mr. Zishu.
- Go away!

80
00:08:14,759 --> 00:08:17,000
Our Liu family, for three generations,
has held official ranks,

81
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,319
with noble carriages at our high gates.

82
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:20,600
Even if I

83
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,360
cannot marry the one I love,

84
00:08:22,879 --> 00:08:25,319
I should at least be matched

85
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,560
with a noble lady of official nobility.

86
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,040
Now I'm forced to accept

87
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,680
you, a merchant's daughter.

88
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,919
It is the greatest humiliation of my life.

89
00:08:35,279 --> 00:08:36,679
You listen well.

90
00:08:37,759 --> 00:08:39,480
This marriage between us

91
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,840
is in name only, not in reality.

92
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,159
From this day forth,

93
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,360
I shall never set foot

94
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,480
in this room again.

95
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,600
It's the wedding night.

96
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,879
How can Liu Chang be so rude

97
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,320
and speak ill words to you

98
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,600
insulting you wantonly?

99
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:08,519
That shouldn't be the behavior
of a gentleman from an official family.

100
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:11,872
My lady.

101
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:13,879
My lady.

102
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:15,840
Don't be too heartbroken.

103
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,720
No matter how the days ahead are spent,

104
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,399
I will always be by your side.

105
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,952
My Lady.

106
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,879
Has Liu Chang left?

107
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:32,720
He's gone. Now

108
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,159
he should have left the courtyard.

109
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,320
Finally gone.

110
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:39,320
If he still didn't leave,

111
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,639
my arms would stiffen from holding up.

112
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:42,759
He didn't hurt you, did he?

113
00:09:43,559 --> 00:09:45,360
I knew you wouldn't be

114
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,240
upset over such an impolite person.

115
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,480
Upset?

116
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,120
I'm too happy to even be upset.

117
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,840
He's not willing to marry me.

118
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:54,639
Am I willing to marry him?

119
00:09:55,519 --> 00:09:56,759
Liu Zishu

120
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,480
is clearly a few years older than me.

121
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,480
But his temperament

122
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,919
is so childish.

123
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,960
Both of us were forced into this marriage.

124
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,440
I haven't even said anything.

125
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,039
Yet he's the one feeling wronged first.

126
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,679
Good Yulu, don't cry.

127
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,960
My mother has taken
the Liu family's tribute medicine.

128
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:25,159
Her complexion has greatly improved.

129
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:28,360
What do I have to be sad about?

130
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,879
Yulu, help me hold this.

131
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:38,919
My lady, where are you going?

132
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,840
It's about to rain, I can't
let my flowers get wet.

133
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,879
My lady, I'll help you.

134
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:45,679
Come on, Yulu, quick, together.

135
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,639
- Lift it up.
- Let's go.

136
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:55,240
Put it here.

137
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,576
Alright.

138
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:06,360
The Liu family treats us so disdainfully.

139
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,320
Life will be tough from now on.

140
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:14,240
After Qiongtai Yulu is soaked in rain,

141
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,960
the leaves become even more
vividly green and elegant.

142
00:11:33,859 --> 00:11:39,059
<i>[Spring of the following year]</i>

143
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:01,960
This jade pendant

144
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,320
has a fine luster.

145
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:06,120
A servant

146
00:12:06,639 --> 00:12:08,639
wearing such an expensive item

147
00:12:09,159 --> 00:12:10,320
isn't proper, is it?

148
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:12,200
Mother,

149
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,399
this jade is nothing extraordinary.

150
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,799
I just think

151
00:12:15,799 --> 00:12:17,600
it matches with Yulu.

152
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,039
So on Yulu's birthday,

153
00:12:19,039 --> 00:12:20,879
it was given as a gift for her to wear.

154
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:25,559
Your He family is
a major medicinal material dealer,

155
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:27,600
naturally looking down on such things.

156
00:12:28,440 --> 00:12:31,039
But if a servant decks out in gold and jade

157
00:12:31,759 --> 00:12:33,879
and it gets seen by outsiders,

158
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:35,200
they might think that our Liu family

159
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,519
throws money around like dirt
and lacks strict management.

160
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:40,160
Take it off.

161
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:44,600
Madam, you are right.

162
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,840
I will take it off as soon as I return.

163
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,159
I'm thinking of Yulu's best interest.

164
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,320
Being too ostentatious

165
00:12:57,879 --> 00:13:00,000
will inevitably lead to gossip.

166
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:03,279
I'll keep this jade pendant safe for now.

167
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,480
On the day Yulu gets married,

168
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:06,960
it will naturally be included in her dowry.

169
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:10,759
Thank you for your concern.

170
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:15,559
As long as you understand my painstaking care.

171
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,519
Recently,

172
00:13:17,519 --> 00:13:20,000
how have you been getting along with Zishu?

173
00:13:20,000 --> 00:13:22,000
Does he still not enter your courtyard?

174
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:24,240
No.

175
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,080
A wife must regard her husband
as her principle.

176
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:29,279
If you cannot win Zishu's affection,

177
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,440
it means you have lost virtue.

178
00:13:32,039 --> 00:13:33,919
Do you understand?

179
00:13:33,919 --> 00:13:36,240
It's my dull and uninteresting nature

180
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,639
that displeases my husband.

181
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:39,840
Please punish me.

182
00:13:40,679 --> 00:13:42,720
I don't want to punish you

183
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,840
but to give you advice.

184
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,200
The Provincial Exam is forthcoming.

185
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:49,440
Although Zishu is already a scholar
with rural contributions,

186
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,240
if a person full of knowledge

187
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:54,759
cannot offer money for connections,

188
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:56,960
it would still be difficult for him
to pass the higher examination smoothly.

189
00:13:58,559 --> 00:14:00,320
As his wife,

190
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:02,240
you ought to make some arrangements for him.

191
00:14:03,399 --> 00:14:05,480
Given my husband's disposition,

192
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,559
I'm afraid he would not agree

193
00:14:06,559 --> 00:14:09,000
to using money to manage official affairs.

194
00:14:10,279 --> 00:14:11,879
Zishu is wholeheartedly devoted to his studies.

195
00:14:11,879 --> 00:14:14,120
He certainly does not understand
these worldly affairs.

196
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:19,039
Mudan,

197
00:14:19,039 --> 00:14:20,720
you come from a merchant family

198
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:24,159
and have a big gap compared to Zishu.

199
00:14:24,159 --> 00:14:25,480
You can only contribute

200
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:26,639
through financial means.

201
00:14:27,639 --> 00:14:29,159
I'm doing this

202
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:32,240
to bring you and your husband
closer together emotionally.

203
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,664
Do you understand?

204
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:36,600
I understand.

205
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,559
Zishu, you're here.

206
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:44,159
Mother.

207
00:14:44,159 --> 00:14:45,559
Come and sit down.

208
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:46,880
Yes.

209
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:52,360
Zishu, you seem
to have lost some weight recently.

210
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:55,360
Preparing for the Imperial Exam
is certainly important.

211
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,519
But you must take good care of your health.

212
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,360
I understand.

213
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:00,759
Thank you for your concern.

214
00:15:01,919 --> 00:15:03,240
Alright, let's eat.

215
00:15:06,080 --> 00:15:07,559
Speaking of the Imperial Exam,

216
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:10,080
every time Mudan visits the Fuyun Temple,

217
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:12,039
she prays for your success.

218
00:15:12,039 --> 00:15:13,440
You should thank her too.

219
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:17,360
The Imperial Exam relies
on genuine knowledge and learning.

220
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,919
There's no need to pray to gods.

221
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:22,519
Does she think I lack talent

222
00:15:22,519 --> 00:15:24,519
and can only rely on the protection of deities?

223
00:15:25,759 --> 00:15:27,240
I did not mean that.

224
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,399
Don't say that.

225
00:15:29,399 --> 00:15:31,600
Mudan is considering your career.

226
00:15:32,399 --> 00:15:33,600
Speaking of your career,

227
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,159
Mudan actually has some thoughts about it.

228
00:15:36,919 --> 00:15:38,559
You can tell your husband now.

229
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,208
Yes.

230
00:15:43,519 --> 00:15:46,200
When you step into officialdom,

231
00:15:46,200 --> 00:15:48,159
it is necessary to manage relations
both above and below

232
00:15:48,159 --> 00:15:49,320
and to make connections with the powerful.

233
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:52,720
I have set aside some money

234
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:54,240
to facilitate your future…

235
00:15:57,519 --> 00:15:59,039
I have studied hard for many years

236
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,440
with the ambition to soar high.

237
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:02,559
After gaining recognition, I will
depend on my own ability

238
00:16:02,559 --> 00:16:03,639
to serve the imperial court.

239
00:16:04,879 --> 00:16:06,200
Do not use your merchant family's

240
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,360
narrow-mindedness

241
00:16:07,360 --> 00:16:08,759
to sully my path to officialdom.

242
00:16:09,919 --> 00:16:12,080
Why have you gotten angry again?

243
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,720
Mudan is thinking of you.

244
00:16:14,799 --> 00:16:16,639
Is she really considering for me

245
00:16:16,639 --> 00:16:18,159
or does she think that I simply cannot

246
00:16:18,159 --> 00:16:19,279
rely on my own talent

247
00:16:19,279 --> 00:16:20,360
to rise straight to the top

248
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,799
and have to depend on these unorthodox methods?

249
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,559
It's not as serious as you think.

250
00:16:25,559 --> 00:16:27,240
If you don't want to, just forget it.

251
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:29,960
I'll persuade Mudan.

252
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,488
Let's eat first.

253
00:16:33,679 --> 00:16:34,960
I will take my leave now.

254
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:44,080
You are

255
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:45,559
quite blunt when you speak.

256
00:16:46,080 --> 00:16:47,080
Can't you say a few soft words

257
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,159
to cajole him a bit?

258
00:16:49,519 --> 00:16:51,440
You saw it.

259
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:53,320
My husband has made up his mind.

260
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:55,720
I suppose further persuasion would be futile.

261
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,568
You…

262
00:16:59,519 --> 00:17:00,879
You have been living in seclusion
for a long time.

263
00:17:00,879 --> 00:17:02,159
You don't understand the ways

264
00:17:02,159 --> 00:17:03,320
of the officialdom.

265
00:17:03,919 --> 00:17:06,200
Zishu is an upright and principled man.

266
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:08,200
He is unwilling to personally give gifts,
seek favor,

267
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:09,759
or win people's hearts.

268
00:17:09,759 --> 00:17:11,599
But for his career,

269
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:13,359
we must plan ahead for him.

270
00:17:14,519 --> 00:17:16,119
But my husband

271
00:17:16,119 --> 00:17:18,119
has just refused.

272
00:17:18,119 --> 00:17:19,400
So what?

273
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:20,799
If you're afraid of displeasing him,

274
00:17:20,799 --> 00:17:22,319
we'll just do it behind his back.

275
