like a cash cow

308
00:18:54,519 --> 00:18:55,599
and proposed a marriage alliance.

309
00:18:55,599 --> 00:18:56,680
But what about them?

310
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:58,839
On the one hand, they ask you for money.

311
00:18:58,839 --> 00:19:00,519
On the other hand, they find fault everywhere.

312
00:19:00,519 --> 00:19:02,599
Liu Chang, even more so, time and time again

313
00:19:02,599 --> 00:19:03,839
comes to humiliate you.

314
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:06,160
And there's this Women's Precepts.

315
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,279
They even want us to hang it up,

316
