317
00:19:08,799 --> 00:19:11,119
This is simply outrageous.

318
00:19:14,599 --> 00:19:16,079
Back then, my mother was gravely ill.

319
00:19:16,799 --> 00:19:18,880
Only the imperial gifted Zixi pills
from the Liu family

320
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,559
