I don't think that's entirely true.

547
00:31:33,599 --> 00:31:36,400
Don't be so angry.

548
00:31:36,400 --> 00:31:37,799
You are the ones I've gone to great lengths

549
00:31:37,799 --> 00:31:38,839
to invite here as honored guests.

550
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:41,559
Why must you torture these scholars?

551
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:46,359
Because it's interesting.

552
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:53,200
What are your plans next?

553
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,640
Will you settle down in the temple?

554
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:59,119
I came here this time

555
00:31:59,119 --> 00:32:00,359
to accompany the County Princess for leisure

556
00:32:00,359 --> 00:32:01,400
by the order of Prince Ning.

557
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:03,960
The County Princess is going to the Liu Mansion

558
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:05,119
to meet her old lover.

559
00:32:05,759 --> 00:32:07,359
Of course, I have to go along.

560
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,759
Looking at it now,

561
00:32:17,759 --> 00:32:19,519
this vile person's family is very interesting.

562
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,720
To not go and meet them

563
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,720
would be a pity.

564
00:32:53,311 --> 00:32:55,840
<i>[To Zishu]</i>

565
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,640
<i>Zishu,</i>

566
00:33:05,640 --> 00:33:06,839
<i>long time no see.</i>

567
00:33:07,359 --> 00:33:08,640
<i>I've missed you very much.</i>

568
00:33:09,200 --> 00:33:10,920
<i>This morning, I took up my pen</i>

569
00:33:10,920 --> 00:33:12,000
<i>with both joy and worry.</i>

570
00:33:12,839 --> 00:33:14,960
<i>I'm glad that my husband has passed away</i>

571
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:16,359
<i>and I finally gained my freedom.</i>

572
00:33:16,960 --> 00:33:19,079
<i>But I'm worried that after years of separation,</i>

573
00:33:19,079 --> 00:33:20,839
<i>I'm unsure of where your heart lies now.</i>

574
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:23,279
<i>The yearning is extremely intense.</i>

575
00:33:23,799 --> 00:33:25,000
<i>Writing cannot fully express my feelings.</i>

576
00:33:26,279 --> 00:33:29,880
<i>Fortunately, soon I shall travel to Luoyang
to ease my mind.</i>

577
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:31,799
<i>I'm calmly awaiting our reunion.</i>

578
00:33:36,359 --> 00:33:37,536
It's been three years.

579
00:33:39,240 --> 00:33:40,640
I never thought that the two of us

580
00:33:41,559 --> 00:33:42,720
could meet again.

581
00:33:49,079 --> 00:33:50,272
Youzhen,

582
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,519
I wonder

583
00:33:53,559 --> 00:33:54,839
what you look like now.

584
00:34:08,039 --> 00:34:09,960
My lady, it's time to apply the medicine.

585
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,040
Okay.

586
00:34:13,599 --> 00:34:15,072
Come on.

587
00:34:17,199 --> 00:34:18,360
Another area has swollen.

588
00:34:20,119 --> 00:34:21,840
Mrs. Liu is truly ruthless.

589
00:34:21,840 --> 00:34:23,920
Kneeling for so long without even being
allowed to use a cushion.

590
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,320
It's not a big deal.

591
00:34:27,320 --> 00:34:28,360
Do you know?

592
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:30,880
Today, when I went to send flowers
to the Grand Celestial Master Hall,

593
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,840
I took the opportunity to make a wish.

594
00:34:32,840 --> 00:34:34,239
I wished that Liu Chang

595
00:34:34,239 --> 00:34:36,559
may go to the toilet without paper
and lose hair while combing.

596
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:39,079
I don't know if the Grand Celestial Master
could manifest his spirit.

597
00:34:39,800 --> 00:34:41,639
Liu Chang is indeed very annoying.

598
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:44,679
You are pressured by Mrs. Liu
to raise money for him.

599
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:45,960
Not only is he ungrateful to you,

600
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:47,159
but he also cursed you.

601
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:48,559
If he were truly noble,

602
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:50,519
he would spit out all the money given as bribes

603
00:34:50,519 --> 00:34:51,679
by your father.

604
00:34:51,679 --> 00:34:54,440
Annoying Liu Chang, Liu Chang is annoying.

605
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,599
Shuai, you're right.

606
00:34:55,599 --> 00:34:56,920
Liu Chang is annoying.

607
00:34:56,920 --> 00:34:57,920
Shuai is the cutest.

608
00:34:59,199 --> 00:35:01,000
Mrs. Liu wants us to smooth relations
in secret without Liu Chang knowing.

609
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,159
If he finds out,

610
00:35:02,159 --> 00:35:03,639
I'm afraid he might take his anger out on you.

611
00:35:04,360 --> 00:35:06,280
Why not simply tell him the whole story?

612
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,719
So what if we tell him?

613
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,639
After all, I am an outsider.

614
00:35:10,639 --> 00:35:12,679
They, mother and son, share a bond.

615
00:35:12,679 --> 00:35:13,960
They won't

616
00:35:13,960 --> 00:35:15,800
fight over me.

617
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:19,039
But you suffer from both sides.

618
00:35:19,039 --> 00:35:20,800
It's too much to bear.

619
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:22,559
You have been lively and smart
since you were little.

620
00:35:22,559 --> 00:35:25,400
Before you were married, you managed
the household accounts orderly and efficiently.

621
00:35:26,679 --> 00:35:28,719
Since marrying into the Liu family,

622
00:35:28,719 --> 00:35:30,440
you've been confined to this small courtyard.

623
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:31,760
Every time you see members of the Liu family,

624
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:33,239
you can only endure insults and humiliation.

625
00:35:35,079 --> 00:35:36,199
I've been kneeling for the whole day.

626
00:35:36,199 --> 00:35:37,440
My legs are numb.

627
00:35:37,440 --> 00:35:39,599
Let me stretch a little.

628
00:35:39,599 --> 00:35:40,960
Come on, Yulu.

629
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:43,648
Catch it.

630
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,639
Being forgotten in this little courtyard

631
00:35:45,639 --> 00:35:47,079
isn't all that bad.

632
00:35:47,840 --> 00:35:50,000
No one disturbs us. It's very peaceful.

633
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,559
Besides, I have you,

634
00:35:51,559 --> 00:35:52,679
these flowers,

635
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:53,960
and Shuai by my side every day.

636
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,760
When there's nothing to do,

637
00:35:55,760 --> 00:35:57,719
I just lift weights
and practice martial arts for fun.

638
00:35:57,719 --> 00:35:59,199
Such days aren't too hard to endure.

639
00:36:00,039 --> 00:36:01,119
As for Liu Chang,

640
00:36:01,719 --> 00:36:03,119
although I dislike him,

641
00:36:03,119 --> 00:36:04,440
I can understand

642
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:05,840
why he treats me this way.

643
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:08,679
Understand? What's there
to understand about him?

644
00:36:08,679 --> 00:36:11,320
He is clearly just a pretentious hypocrite.

645
00:36:12,159 --> 00:36:13,719
Liu Chang

646
00:36:13,719 --> 00:36:15,239
has studied hard for many years

647
00:36:15,239 --> 00:36:16,760
all for the sake of passing the Imperial Exam
with high marks

648
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,039
to bring glory to his family.

649
00:36:18,039 --> 00:36:19,039
This shows

650
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:21,280
he is an ambitious person.

651
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,679
You always say so.

652
00:36:23,679 --> 00:36:25,280
But if he really were that good,

653
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:27,320
you would have fallen for him by now.

654
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:29,280
Fallen for him?

655
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:31,199
That's impossible.

656
00:36:31,199 --> 00:36:32,320
Praise where it's due

657
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,440
and call out what needs to be condemned.

658
00:36:34,039 --> 00:36:35,199
Liu Chang

659
00:36:35,199 --> 00:36:37,159
hates this transactional marriage too much.

660
00:36:37,679 --> 00:36:38,880
It's clearly the fate of the Liu family

661
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:40,000
that forced him to kneel

662
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,159
and the social status

663
00:36:41,159 --> 00:36:42,800
that broke him up with the County Princess.

664
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,199
But he

665
00:36:44,199 --> 00:36:45,599
cannot figure these out

666
00:36:45,599 --> 00:36:47,360
and puts all the anger, resentment,
and unwillingness

667
00:36:47,360 --> 00:36:48,639
upon me.

668
00:36:49,159 --> 00:36:50,400
It shows that this person

669
00:36:50,400 --> 00:36:52,159
is extreme and depressed by nature.

670
00:36:52,159 --> 00:36:53,239
He is unfit to be entrusted
with a lifetime commitment.

671
00:36:54,880 --> 00:36:56,039
Therefore,

672
00:36:56,039 --> 00:36:57,519
we each live our own lives.

673
00:36:57,519 --> 00:36:58,880
Living in peace without issues is very good.

674
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:01,400
You think things through clearly.

675
00:37:02,000 --> 00:37:04,519
In the long years to come,

676
00:37:04,519 --> 00:37:06,920
we'll keep flowers and tease birds together,

677
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,519
enjoying tea and being merry.

678
00:37:08,519 --> 00:37:10,159
Tea drinking is so dull.

679
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:13,440
Go, fetch our wine.

680
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:14,560
Yes.

681
00:37:16,719 --> 00:37:17,888
Shuai.

682
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:20,320
There is nothing to do tomorrow.

683
00:37:20,320 --> 00:37:22,119
Let's drink to our hearts' content.

684
00:37:22,119 --> 00:37:23,264
Okay.

685
00:37:24,199 --> 00:37:25,440
My lady.

686
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:26,639
My lady, something's happened!

687
00:37:26,639 --> 00:37:28,639
My lady, quickly wake up.

688
00:37:28,639 --> 00:37:29,760
What's the matter?

689
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,760
Is it that Mrs. Liu has again asked me

690
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:32,360
to stand by the rules at the family temple

691
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,440
or is there a lack of money in the house again

692
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,599
so that we have to ask my father for it?

693
00:37:35,599 --> 00:37:37,719
County Princess Ji'an
will visit our house tomorrow.

694
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,800
What does it have to do with me?
No need to bother with her.

695
00:37:41,800 --> 00:37:43,239
To receive her, Mr. Liu has people

696
00:37:43,239 --> 00:37:45,119
dig up all the peonies in our courtyard.

697
00:37:47,960 --> 00:37:49,159
When did this happen?

698
00:37:49,159 --> 00:37:51,079
I heard from the servants
that they came to dig last night.

699
00:37:52,159 --> 00:37:53,159
Quick.

700
00:37:53,159 --> 00:37:54,432
Quick.

701
00:38:04,400 --> 00:38:06,119
How did these flowers come to this state?

702
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,880
What kind of gardeners are you?

703
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:10,559
Even moving flowers is too much for you.

704
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:12,280
If the County Princess sees this tomorrow,

705
00:38:12,280 --> 00:38:13,639
both of your heads put together

706
00:38:13,639 --> 00:38:14,960
will not be enough to atone for this.

707
00:38:16,960 --> 00:38:18,320
Father.

708
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,559
Mudan, you have finally come.

709
00:38:19,559 --> 00:38:21,480
Please help me save these flowers.

710
00:38:22,920 --> 00:38:24,280
Father,

711
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,719
if you need flowers,

712
00:38:25,719 --> 00:38:28,000
I can personally go to the flower market
and choose some for you.

713
00:38:28,679 --> 00:38:30,280
Why did you go through the trouble
of digging up my garden's flowers overnight

714
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,519
and bring them all here?

715
00:38:32,800 --> 00:38:34,119
These famous peonies of yours

716
00:38:34,119 --> 00:38:35,480
are extremely precious.

717
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:36,920
The common stock at the flower market

718
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,079
can hardly compare to them.

719
00:38:39,119 --> 00:38:41,840
Moreover, I heard you were drinking last night

720
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,039
and you retired early.

721
00:38:43,039 --> 00:38:45,199
I really couldn't bear to disturb you.

722
00:38:46,039 --> 00:38:47,119
Mudan,

723
00:38:47,119 --> 00:38:48,559
you won't blame me, will you?

724
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,440
I wouldn't dare.

725
00:38:52,440 --> 00:38:55,239
Good child, I originally

726
00:38:55,239 --> 00:38:56,920
didn't want to trouble you
to take action personally.

727
00:38:57,679 --> 00:38:59,000
But I didn't expect these peonies of yours

728
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,679
to be so delicate.

729
00:39:00,679 --> 00:39:01,760
The gardeners I hired

730
00:39:01,760 --> 00:39:02,920
simply can't take good care of them.

731
00:39:03,559 --> 00:39:05,000
Mudan, take a look.

732
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:06,000
Can they still be saved?

733
00:39:09,559 --> 00:39:10,559
Mudan,

734
00:39:10,559 --> 00:39:12,360
you must save them.

735
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,360
The distinguished guests visiting tomorrow

736
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:16,280
include not only the beloved daughter
of Prince Ning,

737
00:39:16,280 --> 00:39:17,320
County Princess Ji'an,

738
00:39:17,320 --> 00:39:19,320
and the favored court figure Jiang Changyang.

739
00:39:20,079 --> 00:39:22,280
You may not know about it
living inside the mansion.

740
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:23,400
Jiang Changyang

741
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,280
is not only the Vice Minister
of the Office of Imperial Ceremonies

742
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:27,559
but also serves as the Floral Envoy.

743
00:39:27,559 --> 00:39:28,840
He collects rare and exotic treasures
for the emperor

744
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:31,360
from all over the world.

745
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:34,519
If they find no flowers at the feast tomorrow,

746
00:39:34,519 --> 00:39:35,840
it would be tantamount
to deceiving the emperor.

747
00:39:35,840 --> 00:39:37,199
Everyone in our Liu family

748
00:39:37,199 --> 00:39:38,440
will be implicated.

749
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,480
Father, there's no need for further words.

750
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,760
No matter who comes to the mansion tomorrow,

751
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:44,159
I don't care.

752
00:39:44,159 --> 00:39:46,639
What do you mean by this?

753
00:39:46,639 --> 00:39:48,679
These peonies were my mother's legacy to me.

754
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:50,760
Regardless of whether the nobles come tomorrow

755
00:39:50,760 --> 00:39:52,159
or whether the floral banquet is held,

756
00:39:52,159 --> 00:39:53,880
I will do my utmost to save them.

757
00:39:55,639 --> 00:39:57,119
Alright.

758
00:39:57,119 --> 00:39:59,480
As long as you can revive these flowers

759
00:39:59,480 --> 00:40:01,480
and make tomorrow's honored guests satisfied,

760
00:40:01,480 --> 00:40:04,480
you can choose from the rare treasures
in the mansion as you like after the banquet.

761
00:40:09,039 --> 00:40:10,719
These peonies are my treasures.

762
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,559
As long as they are well,

763
00:40:13,239 --> 00:40:14,360
I desire nothing else.

764
00:40:15,599 --> 00:40:16,960
Work on them with peace of mind.

765
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:18,159
If you have any requests,

766
00:40:18,159 --> 00:40:19,760
just give the order.

767
00:40:19,760 --> 00:40:21,599
Yulu, go get

768
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:22,599
the stored flower fertilizer

769
00:40:22,599 --> 00:40:23,960
and the original soil in our courtyard.

770
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,248
Yes.

771
00:40:26,039 --> 00:40:28,159
You two, these flowers must be irrigated
with well water

772
00:40:28,159 --> 00:40:29,800
that has been set aside for two days.

773
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:32,079
If there isn't enough stored water
in the courtyard,

774
00:40:32,079 --> 00:40:33,280
you have to go outside the courtyard

775
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,639
and fetch two buckets of river water.

776
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:37,840
- Do you understand?
- Yes.

777
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,008
Go quickly.

778
00:40:40,239 --> 00:40:41,360
Excuse me, Father, please step aside.

