fills the fragrant garden ♫</i>

809
00:44:05,619 --> 00:44:12,921
<i>♫ With a heart as my lantern,
I don't mind the distant mountain paths ♫</i>

810
00:44:13,605 --> 00:44:21,914
<i>♫ The flute's sound,
a fleeting life's wishes fulfilled ♫</i>

811
